OL,4,Cofficers after anti-corruption hotline
OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,FMore than 700 investigations have been
OL,8,Flaunched by Britain's biggest police
OL,9,Fforce after nearly 3,000 contacts to
OL,10,Fan anti-corruption hotline in the
OL,11,Ffirst 18 months of operation.
OL,13,FThe figures for the were revealed on
OL,14,FThursday as the police anti-corruption
OL,15,Fand abuse reporting service was rolled
OL,16,Fout nationally.
