OL,3,COver 700 investigations into Met
OL,4,Cofficers after anti-corruption hotline
OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,FA series of harrowing scandals,
OL,8,Fincluding the murder of Sarah Everard
OL,9,Fby serving officer Wayne Couzens, and
OL,10,Fthen-Pc David Carrick being unmasked
OL,11,Fas a serial rapist, led to be the
OL,12,Ffirst force to start using the service
OL,13,Fin November 2022.
OL,15,FIt will now be available for reports
OL,16,Fabout all UK police forces, either
OL,17,Fonline or by calling 0800 085 0000,
OL,18,Fand will be run by the independent
OL,19,Fcharity Crimestoppers, which will
OL,20,Fallow anonymous tip-offs.
