OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,FInformation can be passed on about
OL,8,Fpotential crimes including police
OL,9,Fofficers, staff or volunteers who may
OL,10,Fbe accepting bribes, abusing their
OL,11,Fposition, mistreating their partner or
OL,12,Fexpressing racist, homophobic,
OL,13,Fmisogynistic or disablist beliefs.
OL,15,FDetails will be passed on to the
OL,16,Frelevant force for assessment and may
OL,17,Flead to an investigation.
