OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,FSo far for the Met, since November
OL,8,F2022, there have been 1,988 calls and
OL,9,F890 online reports, with 867 pieces of
OL,10,Fintelligence passed onto the force.
OL,12,FThis has led to 728 Met
OL,13,Finvestigations, and the remaining 139
OL,14,Freports were passed to other relevant
OL,15,Fpolice forces.
