OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,FWith both Wayne Couzens and Carrick, a
OL,8,Fseries of opportunities were missed to
OL,9,Froot out their abhorrent behaviour,
OL,10,Fshaking public confidence in the
OL,11,Fpolice service to find wrongdoing in
OL,12,Fits own ranks.
OL,14,FVarious other scandals also severely
OL,15,Fdamaged the Met's reputation,
OL,16,Fincluding two officers who were jailed
OL,17,Ffor sharing pictures of the bodies of
OL,18,Ftwo murdered sisters, and deeply
OL,19,Foffensive and disturbing messages
OL,20,Fshared among some officers in WhatsApp
OL,21,Fgroups.
