OL,4,Cofficers after anti-corruption hotline
OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,F"We do not underestimate the impact
OL,8,Frecent events have had on trust and
OL,9,Fconfidence in policing, including the
OL,10,Fappalling findings of the Angiolini
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,F"We have made progress in
OL,14,Fstrengthening procedures around
OL,15,Fmisconduct and vetting, and forces are
OL,16,Ftaking a proactive approach to finding
OL,17,Fand rooting out wrongdoing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
