OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,F"However, we know there is always more
OL,8,Fto do to ensure that we meet the high
OL,9,Fstandards rightly expected and
OL,10,Fdeserved by the public.
OL,12,F"The vast majority of police officers
OL,13,Fand staff act professionally and with
OL,14,Fintegrity in the fulfilment of their
OL,15,Fduties to protect the public. We must
OL,16,Ftake tough action to purge policing of
OL,17,Fthose responsible for wrongdoing, for
OL,18,Fnow and for the future.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
