OL,5,Claunches
OL,7,F"This year, we checked our entire
OL,8,Fworkforce for unknown allegations or
OL,9,Fconcerns and will begin long-term
OL,10,Fscreening to ensure that there is no
OL,11,Fplace for corrupt or abusive officers
OL,12,Fand staff to hide in our forces."
OL,14,FPolicing minister Chris Philp said:
OL,15,F"Public confidence in our police has
OL,16,Fbeen severely damaged.
OL,18,F"There can be no stone left unturned
OL,19,Fin our efforts to clean up the
OL,20,Fworkforce and culture, and rebuild
OL,21,Ftrust.
